# Slack channel: app and bot tokens. Core connection: use channels/.env (core_host, core_port, CORE_API_KEY).
# Create app at api.slack.com; enable Socket Mode; create app-level token (xapp-...) and bot token (xoxb-...).
# Copy to .env and set tokens (or set in channels/.env).
SLACK_APP_TOKEN=xapp-...
SLACK_BOT_TOKEN=xoxb-...
